{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"171947-wambuzi-wambwa-ne-wante","title":"Wambuzi, Wambwa ne Wante","description":"Find out why the dog runs towards a car and a goat away from it!","language":"Luganda","langCode":"lg","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Martha Nansamba"],"illustrators":["Marleen  Visser"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/171947-wambuzi-wambwa-ne-wante"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/230914/size3/7c81e4686ebc12ac21d75f2fb9275243.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/230914/size6/7c81e4686ebc12ac21d75f2fb9275243.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229559/size6/696a4cde242fd1345c447c05d4d61ce3.jpg","text":"Wambuzi, Wambwa ne\nWante baali ba mukwano\nnnyo.\nOlumu baagenda ku\nlugendo mu takisi.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229561/size6/159e0859bd05f883a099d60b967267d3.jpg","text":"Bwe baatuuka gye balaga,\nomugoba w'emmotoka\nnaabasaba basasule\nssente.\nWante yasasula ezize.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229563/size6/27be21a45a31a6c4af8ba391b2859b2a.jpg","text":"Wambwa yasasula\nezisinga ku ze yali alina\nokusasula, kubanga\nteyalina muwendo gwa\nssente gwennyini.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229565/size6/99ab5e99a86fa9fa0e946cb0fabf8269.jpg","text":"Omugoba w'emmotoka\nyali anaatera okuddiza\nWambwa ssente ze.\nNaye Wambuzi n'atandika\nokudduka ate nga\ntasasudde.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229566/size6/f7b8377e11e2ebc1c722bfe23dd2ce05.jpg","text":"Omugoba yanyiiga nnyo.\nEra n'agenda nga taddizza\nWambwa ssente ze.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229569/size6/2b544b24a81eb41a86c118c4dfd67879.jpg","text":"Ky'ova olaba n'okutuusa\nleero, Wambwa adduka\nokulingiza mu mmotoka.\nAlabe omugoba omuvuzi\nw'emmotoka alina ssente\nze.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229571/size6/5cbfaf88f8247e98c59cd73aadfce9f3.jpg","text":"Ate ye Wambuzi\nbw'awulira emmotoka ejja.\nAdduka kubanga atya nti\nbayinza okumukwata\nolw'obutasasula.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229574/size6/6d813ebd24fa53e4cd6cb57ed8e16e58.jpg","text":"Wante ye tafaayo oba\nemmotoka ne bw'eba ejja.\nAsala ekkubo nga\nyeetwala anti akimanyi nti\nyasasula n'amalayo.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":111}}